\c 3
\s UBhowazi uvuma ukuba ngumhlengi
\p
\v 1 UNawomi uninazala wasesithi kuye: Ndodakazi yami, ngingakudingeli ukuphumula\x + 1.9.\x* yini ukuze kube kuhle kuwe?
\v 2 Ngakho-ke uBhowazi ayisuye wezihlobo\x + 2.1.\x* zethu yini, obulamantombazana akhe\x + 2.8.\x*? Khangela, wela \w ibhali\w** ebaleni lokubhulela ngalobubusuku.
\v 3 Ngakho geza uzigcobe\x + 2 Sam. 14.2.\x*, ugqoke isembatho sakho, wehlele ebaleni lokubhulela; ungazivezi endodeni ize iqede ukudla lokunatha.
\v 4 Kuzakuthi-ke lapho eselala, uqaphelise indawo alala kiyo, ungene, ubususembula inyawo zakhe, ulale phansi; yena-ke uzakutshela ozakwenza.
\v 5 Wasesithi kuye: Konke okutshoyo kimi ngizakwenza.
\p
\v 6 Wasesehlela ebaleni lokubhulela, wenza njengakho konke ayemlaye khona uninazala.
\v 7 Kwathi uBhowazi esedlile wanatha, lenhliziyo yakhe yathokoza\x + Hlu. 19.6.\x*, wayalala phansi ekucineni kwenqumbi yamabele. \add URuthe\add* wasenyenya\x + Hlu. 4.21.\x*, wembula inyawo zakhe, walala phansi.
\p
\v 8 Kwasekusithi phakathi kobusuku indoda yethuka, yaphenduka, khangela-ke owesifazana elele enyaweni zayo.
\v 9 Yathi: Ungubani? Wasesithi: NginguRuthe incekukazi yakho; ngakho yendlala umphetho wesembatho sakho phezu kwencekukazi yakho\x + Hez. 16.8. Dute. 22.30.\x*, ngoba ungumhlengi.
\v 10 Yasisithi: \add Ka\add*wubusiswe yiN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 2.20.\x*, ndodakazi yami, usuwenze umusa wakho ube mkhulu ekucineni kulowokuqala\x + 1.8.\x*, njengoba ungalandelanga amajaha loba angabayanga loba anothileyo.
\v 11 Ngakho-ke, ndodakazi yami, ungesabi, ngizakwenzela konke okutshoyo, ngoba umuzi wonke wabantu bakithi uyazi ukuthi ungowesifazana oqotho\x + Zaga 12.4; 31.10.\x*.
\v 12 Yebo-ke, sibili, kuliqiniso ukuthi ngiyisihlobo esingumhlengi\x + 3.9.\x*, kanti-ke kukhona isihlobo esingumhlengi esiseduze kulami\x + 4.1.\x*.
\v 13 Hlala lobubusuku; kuzakuthi-ke ekuseni uba ezakwenza imfanelo yesihlobo esingumhlengi\x + 4.5. Dute. 25.5.\x*, kulungile, kakuhlenge; kodwa uba engathandi ukukuhlenga, mina-ke ngizakuhlenga, kuphila kukaJehova\x + Hlu. 8.19. 1 Sam. 14.39; 19.6; 20.3,21; 25.26,34; 26.10,16; 28.10; 29.6. 2 Sam. 12.5. 2 Kho. 2.2,6. Jer. 4.2; 5.2.\x*. Lala kuze kuse.
\p
\v 14 Waselala enyaweni zayo kwaze kwasa\x + 3.8.\x*; wavuka omunye engakananzeleli omunye. Yasisithi: Kakungaziwa ukuthi owesifazana ufikile ebaleni lokubhulela.
\v 15 Yasisithi: Letha isembatho osigqokileyo, usibambe; wasesibamba, yasilinganisa \add izilinganiso\add* eziyisithupha \w zebhali\w**, yamethesa; wasengena emzini.
\v 16 Kwathi esefike kuninazala, wathi: Ungubani, ndodakazi yami? Wasemtshela konke indoda eyayimenzele khona.
\v 17 Wathi: Ingiphe lezi\add zilinganiso\add* eziyisithupha zebhali, ngoba ithe kimi: Ungayi kunyokozala ungelalutho.
\v 18 Wasesithi: Hlala\x + Isa. 30.7. Hlab. 37.3,5.\x*, ndodakazi yami, uze wazi ukuthi udaba luzaphetha njani, ngoba indoda kayiyikuphumula ize iluqede udaba lamuhla.